{"tid":491022,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港做女人真係好","createTime":"2017-12-06T06:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T12:27:31.000Z","uid":79793,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"50569fa70807dae7c85be04222acf725c20ee0a6","tid":491022,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我有位朋友係一個情痴，佢一愛上一個人就會痴哂線<br />\n咁佢就上左一間女僕Cafe，識左一個女仔，起初都冇咩野，我睇我個朋友都好開心，咁都冇阻止佢溝女。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慢慢佢地關係開始曖昧，又抱又錫，條女仲一直暗示已經係情侶關係<br />\n但係我個朋友都冇佢電話，剩係可以用Facebook傾計，原因就係話工作問題，唔比得電話，我果一下已經屌左我個fd，但係佢已經好似沉左船咁，番唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條女開始利用我朋友既毒撚性格，一直比假希望佢，我朋友仲送哂禮物，幫佢做左好多野，又請食飯，又做跑腿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始比哂假希望，然後我朋友一表白就比佢一腳踢開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位巴打，唔好亂信班女人<br />\n班女人好古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我的朋友不是我</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0031fae04c02855c120265cf35badb86ce85426b","tid":491022,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c46c59fb0161d59363a4174ba4d8348cda0b1df","tid":491022,"uid":56626,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"一早講咗搞基係至好"},{"pid":"71ddb25c8827619e78a28052b60ab9a993c32fb6","tid":491022,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早講咗搞基係至好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tong